@startuml
title Hình 3.1: Tổng quan quy trình kiểm thử tự động Web UI

actor Tester

component "Pytest\n(Test Framework)" as Pytest
component "Playwright\n(Automation Tool)" as Playwright
component "Browser\n(Chromium / Firefox / WebKit)" as Browser
component "OrangeHRM\n(Web Application)" as App
component "Result\n(Screenshot / Video / Trace)" as Result

Tester --> Pytest : Write & Run Tests
Pytest --> Playwright : Execute Test Steps
Playwright --> Browser : Control Browser
Browser --> App : Interact UI
App --> Browser : Response
Browser --> Playwright : UI State
Playwright --> Pytest : Test Status
Pytest --> Result : Generate Report

@enduml
